{"type":"message","id":"32995c0a","parentId":"7786ea65","timestamp":"2026-02-22T15:59:38.034Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### **步骤3：创建安装监控脚本**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Pgezly7EianNaNkwTmdtJsBO","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\WH\\Desktop\\监控微信安装.bat","content":"@echo off\nchcp 65001 >nul\necho.\necho ========================================\necho       微信安装监控工具\necho ========================================\necho.\n\necho 安装状态监控中...\necho 按 Ctrl+C 可以停止监控\necho.\n\n:loop\nREM 检查安装进程\ntasklist /FI \"IMAGENAME eq WeChatSetup.exe\" 2>nul | find /I \"WeChatSetup.exe\" >nul\nif %errorlevel% equ 0 (\n    echo [%time%] 安装程序正在运行...\n) else (\n    echo [%time%] 安装程序未运行\n)\n\nREM 检查微信进程\ntasklist /FI \"IMAGENAME eq WeChat.exe\" 2>nul | find /I \"WeChat.exe\" >nul\nif %errorlevel% equ 0 (\n    echo [%time%] 微信正在运行...\n)\n\nREM 检查微信版本文件\nif exist \"C:\\Program Files\\Tencent\\WeChat\\WeChat.exe\" (\n    for %%F in (\"C:\\Program Files\\Tencent\\WeChat\\WeChat.exe\") do (\n        echo [%time%] 微信文件大小: %%~zF 字节\n    )\n)\n\necho.\ntimeout /t 10 /nobreak >nul\ncls\ngoto loop"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":218,"output":362,"cacheRead":73088,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73668,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771775969922}}
