{"type":"message","id":"0449f5e5","parentId":"0ddcb522","timestamp":"2026-02-22T15:59:57.412Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"NSIS错误！这是安装程序文件损坏或下载不完整的问题。让我帮你解决这个问题。\n\n## 🔧 **NSIS错误解决方案**\n\nNSIS (Nullsoft Scriptable Install System) 错误通常是因为：\n1. 安装文件下载不完整\n2. 安装文件损坏\n3. 内存或磁盘问题\n4. 杀毒软件干扰\n\n### **立即解决方案：**\n\n#### **步骤1：重新下载微信安装包**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_wZ8NWi5LLwhBtzcPERLnO8o8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 删除损坏的安装文件并重新下载\n$installerPath = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Desktop\\WeChatSetup.exe\"\n\nWrite-Host \"删除损坏的安装文件...\"\nif (Test-Path $installerPath) {\n    Remove-Item $installerPath -Force\n    Write-Host \"已删除: $installerPath\"\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"`n重新下载微信安装包...\"\nWrite-Host \"使用备用下载链接...\"\n\n# 尝试多个下载源\n$downloadUrls = @(\n    \"https://dldir1.qq.com/weixin/Windows/WeChatSetup.exe\",  # 官方主链接\n    \"https://webcdn.m.qq.com/spcmgr/download/WeChatSetup.exe\",  # 备用链接1\n    \"https://down.qq.com/qqweb/WeChat/WeChatSetup.exe\"  # 备用链接2\n)\n\n$success = $false\nforeach ($url in $downloadUrls) {\n    try {\n        Write-Host \"尝试下载: $url\"\n        Invoke-WebRequest -Uri $url -OutFile $installerPath -TimeoutSec 30\n        $fileSize = (Get-Item $installerPath).Length\n        Write-Host \"下载成功! 文件大小: $([math]::Round($fileSize/1MB, 2)) MB\"\n        \n        if ($fileSize -gt 8000000) {  # 大于8MB才认为是完整文件\n            $success = $true\n            break\n        } else {\n            Write-Host \"文件大小异常，可能不完整\"\n            Remove-Item $installerPath -Force\n        }\n    } catch {\n        Write-Host \"下载失败: $_\"\n    }\n}\n\nif ($success) {\n    Write-Host \"`n✅ 微信安装包下载完成\"\n    Write-Host \"位置: $installerPath\"\n} else {\n    Write-Host \"`n❌ 所有下载源都失败\"\n    Write-Host \"请手动访问: https://pc.weixin.qq.com/\"\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":69,"output":577,"cacheRead":73920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74566,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"c