undColor Cyan\n            Write-Host \"3. 安装时暂时关闭杀毒软件\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n        } else {\n            Write-Host \"⚠️ 文件大小可能仍然不完整\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n            Write-Host \"建议使用浏览器直接下载\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n        }\n    }\n    \n} catch {\n    Write-Host \"`n❌ 下载失败: $_\" -ForegroundColor Red\n    Write-Host \"`n备用方案:\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    Write-Host \"1. 访问 https://pc.weixin.qq.com/\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    Write-Host \"2. 使用浏览器直接下载\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    Write-Host \"3. 不要使用下载工具\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"`n\" + \"=\" * 50\nWrite-Host \"按任意键退出...\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n$null = $Host.UI.RawUI.ReadKey(\"NoEcho,IncludeKeyDown\")"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":53,"output":850,"cacheRead":76480,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77383,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771776114861}}
